Requirements:

2Pong was coded using python3 and pygame on a windows operating system. If you 
wish to play 2Pong you will need python as well as pygame. You can download 
python from https://www.python.org/downloads/ 

Once python is installed, open a command prompt and run the following command:
pip install pygame

Once python and pygame are both installed you should be able to run and play
2Pong
